Name: Kumar Sparsh
Reviews: Must try their garlic bread and don't forget to try that heavenly topping !Pizzas are okay from a pre made base pizza base standards. not too great.

Name: Abhishek Padmasale
Reviews: Not a great choice of pizzas available. However, the quality of toppings is good. It's OK for a quick bite.

Reviews: Decent but not worth going again

Reviews: Good for garlic bread...value for money.
